Package: gammarus.phosphorum
Title: Population-level Tests of the Growth Rate Hypothesis in Gammarus
    fossarum
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Titouan", 
        family = "Dionet",
        role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
        email = "titouan.dionet@univ-lorraine.fr",
        comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-5602-1873")))
Description: Companion code to Dionet et al. (in prep.) Testing the Growth 
    Rate Hypothesis at the population level: fast growing populations of 
    Gammarus fossarum do not necessarily exhibit the highest phosphorus 
    contents. Provides functions for size-structured matrix population 
    modeling, stoichiometric calculations, and simulation tools to explore 
    the relationship between population growth rate and phosphorus content. 
    Raw data are archived separately https://doi.org/10.57745/KTUAUG. The 
    manuscript is available as a preprint https://hal.science/hal-05641762.
